title: VW Jetta ~2013 Manuals.tar.gz
description:
A whole lot of PDFs containing tech tips, wiring diagrams, troubleshooting guides, part number lists focused on the 2013 Jetta TDI.

Linux users should be able to open easy with tar or any archive manager.
Windows users can use 7z I think to extract contents.

If you can't get past the three pages that show what a warning, caution, and note is, use some other PDF reader than Adobe Reader. I use evince on Ubuntu, and I don't get trapped
